dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Alexander Perez. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Rose. Could you provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Yes, my policy number is five six eight nine two and my date of birth is zero five one two one nine eight seven.
Thank you, Rose, for providing that information. Can you also confirm the make and model of your vehicle for our records?
Sure, I drive a silver Honda Civic.
Great, thank you for that. Is there anything specific you would like to discuss regarding your policy, Rose?
I wanted to inquire about adding roadside assistance to my coverage.
Of course, Rose. Let me assist you with that request. Thank you for reaching out today.
Thank you for your time, Rose. Have a wonderful day.
